#: ../../content/applications/websites.rst:5
msgid "Websites"
msgstr "網站"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:3
msgid "Blog"
msgstr "網誌"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Odoo Blog** lets you manage blog pages and posts, and customize them with "
"the website builder."
msgstr "**Odoo 部落格**讓您管理部落格頁面和貼文，並使用網站建立器自訂它們。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:8
msgid ""
"Install the :guilabel:`Blog` app by clicking :guilabel:`New` on the website "
"builder, then selecting  :guilabel:`Blog Post`, and "
"clicking :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr ""
"在網站建立器上按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ ，然後選擇\\ :guilabel:`部落格貼"
"文`\\ ，並按一下\\ :guilabel:`安裝`\\ ，以安裝\\ :guilabel:`部落格`\\ 應用程"
"式。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:12
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Blogs [video] <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"blogs-6935>`_"
msgstr "`Odoo 教學：部落格 [影片] <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/blogs-6935>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:15
msgid "Blog posts"
msgstr "部落格文章"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:17
msgid ""
"To create a blog post, click :guilabel:`New` on the website builder and "
"click :guilabel:`Blog Post`. Select a :ref:`blog <blog/blog-pages>`, define "
"a :guilabel:`Blog Post Title`, and click :guilabel:`Save`. Write the post's "
"content and customize it using the website builder."
msgstr ""
"若要建立部落格文章，請按一下網站編輯器上的\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 並按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`部落格文章`\\ 。選取一個\\ :ref:`部落格 <blog/blog-pages>`\\ ，定"
"義\\ :guilabel:`部落格文章標題`\\ ，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存`\\ 。撰寫文"
"章內容並使用網站編輯器進行自訂。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:21
msgid ""
"To publish a post, toggle the :guilabel:`Unpublished` switch in the top-"
"right corner of the page."
msgstr "若要發佈文章，請切換頁面右上角的\\ :guilabel:`未發佈`\\ 開關。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:23
msgid ""
"To delete a blog post, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Blog "
"post`. Select the blog post to delete, click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, and :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`Delete`."
msgstr ""
"若要刪除部落格文章，請前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 網站 --> 部落格文章`\\ "
"。選取要刪除的部落格文章，按一下\\ :icon:`fa-cog`\\ :guilabel:`動作`\\ ，然後"
"按\\ :icon:`fa-trash-o`\\ :guilabel:`刪除`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:27
msgid "Customize blog posts"
msgstr "自訂部落格文章"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:29
msgid ""
"To customize the layout of all blog posts, open one and "
"click :menuselection:`Edit --> Style`. Under the :guilabel:`Blog page` "
"section, different options can be used to customize the posts:"
msgstr ""
"若要自訂所有部落格文章的版面配置，請開啟一篇文章並按一下\\ :menuselection:`編"
"輯 --> 樣式`\\ 。在\\ :guilabel:`部落格頁面`\\ 區段下，可以使用不同的選項來自"
"訂文章："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:32
msgid ":guilabel:`Layout`: display the title inside or above the cover."
msgstr ":guilabel:`版面配置`：在封面內部或上方顯示標題。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Increase Readability`: adjust or not the posts' formatting for "
"better reading comfort."
msgstr ":guilabel:`提高可讀性`：調整或不調整文章的格式以提升閱讀舒適度。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sidebar`: display or hide a sidebar that can contain several "
"elements:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`側邊欄`：顯示或隱藏可包含多個元素的側邊欄："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Archive`: allow visitors to view all posts from a specific month "
"by selecting it."
msgstr ":guilabel:`封存`：允許訪客透過選取特定月份來檢視該月份的所有文章。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:37
msgid ":guilabel:`Author`: display the post author."
msgstr ":guilabel:`作者`：顯示文章作者。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:38
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Blog List`: display links to all :ref:`blog pages <blog/blog-"
"pages>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`部落格清單`：顯示所有\\ :ref:`部落格頁面 <blog/blog-pages>`\\ 的連"
"結。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Share Links`: add clickable icons that link to your social "
"network profiles and a subscription field for your newsletter."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`分享連結`：加入可按一下的圖示，連結至您的社群網路個人檔案，以及電"
"子報的訂閱欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: create or select existing :ref:`tags <blog/tags>` and "
"display them on the post."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`標籤`：建立或選取現有的\\ :ref:`標籤 <blog/tags>`\\ 並在文章上顯示"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:43
msgid ":guilabel:`Breadcrumb`: display the breadcrumb trail."
msgstr ":guilabel:`導覽列`：顯示導覽路徑。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bottom`: click the :guilabel:`Next Article` to hide or display "
"the next post at the end of the page, and click :guilabel:`Comments` to "
"enable or disable visitors' comments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`底部`：按一下\\ :guilabel:`下一篇文章`\\ 以隱藏或顯示頁面末尾的下"
"一篇文章，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`留言`\\ 以啟用或停用訪客留言。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:47
msgid ""
"To add tags or customize the cover of a specific post, click the cover and "
"use the following settings under the :guilabel:`Blog Post Cover` section:"
msgstr ""
"若要加入標籤或自訂特定文章的封面，請按一下封面並在\\ :guilabel:`部落格文章封"
"面`\\ 區段下使用以下設定："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Tags`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`標籤`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Background`: add an image by clicking the :icon:`os-"
"camera` :guilabel:`(camera)` icon, or use a background color by clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-ban` (:guilabel:`None`) icon and selecting a color."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`背景`：按一下\\ :icon:`os-camera`\\ :guilabel:`（相機）`\\ 圖示加"
"入圖片，或按一下\\ :icon:`fa-ban`（:guilabel:`無`）圖示並選取顏色來使用背景顏"
"色。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Size`: select the size of the cover (:guilabel:`Full "
"screen`, :guilabel:`Half screen`, or :guilabel:`Fit text`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`尺寸`：選擇封面的尺寸（:guilabel:`全螢幕`、:guilabel:`半螢"
"幕`或:guilabel:`符合文字`）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Filter Intensity`: choose the cover filter's intensity "
"(:guilabel:`Low`, :guilabel:`Medium`, :guilabel:`High`) or disable it by "
"selecting :guilabel:`No filter`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`濾鏡強度`：選擇封面濾鏡的強度"
"（:guilabel:`低`、:guilabel:`中`、:guilabel:`高`），或選擇\\ :guilabel:`無濾"
"鏡`\\ 來停用。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:61
#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:153
msgid "After applying the desired changes, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "套用所需變更後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:64
msgid ""
"Illustrate your posts with copyright-free images from :doc:`Unsplash </"
"applications/general/integrations/unsplash>`."
msgstr ""
"使用來自\\ :doc:`Unsplash </applications/general/integrations/unsplash>`\\ 的"
"免版稅圖片來說明您的文章。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:66
msgid ""
"Use :ref:`Plausible <analytics/plausible>` to track traffic on your blog."
msgstr "使用\\ :ref:`Plausible <analytics/plausible>`\\ 追蹤您部落格上的流量。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:67
msgid ""
"Customize blog building blocks through the website editor. For example, "
"filter by the :guilabel:`Latest blog posts` or :guilabel:`Most viewed blog "
"posts` and determine which blog to display in the building block."
msgstr ""
"透過網站編輯器自訂部落格建構模組。例如，依\\ :guilabel:`最新部落格文章`\\ "
"或\\ :guilabel:`最多瀏覽的部落格文章`\\ 篩選，並決定要在建構模組中顯示哪個部"
"落格。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:72
msgid ""
":doc:`Building block documentation <website/web_design/building_blocks>`"
msgstr ":doc:`建構模組使用說明 <website/web_design/building_blocks>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/blog.rst:73
msgid ":doc:`Odoo rich-text editor documentation <../essentials/html_editor>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Odoo 豐富文字編輯器使用說明 <../essentials/html_editor>`"

