#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:137
msgid "Product combos"
msgstr "產品組合"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:139
msgid ""
":ref:`Product combinations <pos/products/combos>` allow users to configure a "
"set of related products to buy as a bundle. To :ref:`configure combos <pos/"
"products/combo-choices>`, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Combo Choices`. Once finished and published, customers can choose the combo "
"when adding the product to the cart. Depending on the configuration, certain "
"items may incur an additional charge."
msgstr ""
":ref:`產品組合 <pos/products/combos>`\\ 允許使用者配置一組相關產品以組合方式"
"購買。若要\\ :ref:`配置組合 <pos/products/combo-choices>`，請前往\\ "
":menuselection:`網站 --> 電子商務 --> 組合選擇`。完成並發布後，客戶可以在將產"
"品加入購物車時選擇組合。根據配置，某些項目可能會產生額外費用。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:None
msgid "Add the combo product to the cart."
msgstr "將組合產品加入購物車。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:152
msgid "Cross-selling & Upselling"
msgstr "交叉銷售與向上銷售"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:154
msgid ""
"Cross-selling and upselling are sales techniques used to present customers "
"with additional or higher-tier products and services from the :doc:`catalog "
"<../../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>`. Cross-selling focuses on "
"recommending accessory or :doc:`optional products </applications/sales/sales/"
"sales_quotations/optional_products>` alongside the item being purchased "
"during ordering and checkout. Upselling, on the other hand, encourages "
"customers to choose a higher-priced or upgraded alternative product."
msgstr ""
"交叉銷售和向上銷售是銷售技巧，用於向客戶展示\\ :doc:`目錄 <../../ecommerce/"
"ecommerce_design/catalog>`\\ 中的額外或更高級產品和服務。交叉銷售著重於在訂購"
"和結帳期間，隨同所購買的項目推薦配件或\\ :doc:`選配產品 </applications/sales/"
"sales/sales_quotations/optional_products>`\\ 。另一方面，向上銷售鼓勵客戶選擇"
"價格更高或升級的替代產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:161
msgid ""
"To configure these product suggestions, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select the relevant product, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, and add the desired products in the "
"corresponding :guilabel:`Optional products`, :guilabel:`Accessory Products`, "
"and/or :guilabel:`Alternative products` fields."
msgstr ""
"若要配置這些產品建議，請前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 電子商務 --> 產品`\\ "
"，選擇相關產品，前往\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 分頁，然後在對應的\\ :guilabel:`選"
"配產品`\\ 、\\ :guilabel:`配件產品`\\ 和/或\\ :guilabel:`替代產品`\\ 欄位中加"
"入所需產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:168
msgid "Optional products"
msgstr "可選產品"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:170
msgid ""
"Optional products are suggested when the customer clicks the :guilabel:`Add "
"to cart` button to buy a specific product."
msgstr ""
"當客戶按一下\\ :guilabel:`加入購物車`\\ 按鈕購買特定產品時，系統會建議選配產"
"品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:0
msgid "Optional products cross-selling."
msgstr "選購產品交叉銷售。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:176
msgid "Accessory products"
msgstr "配件產品"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:178
msgid ""
"Accessory products appear in the :guilabel:`Suggested accessories` section "
"during the :guilabel:`Order summary` step, just prior to proceeding to "
"checkout."
msgstr ""
"配件產品會在\\ :guilabel:`訂單摘要`\\ 步驟的\\ :guilabel:`建議配件`\\ 區段中"
"顯示，就在進入結帳程序之前。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:0
msgid "Suggested accessories at checkout during cart review"
msgstr "在購物車檢視期間結帳時建議的配件"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:185
msgid ""
"To hide this section, open the :doc:`website editor <../../website/"
"web_design>`, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Suggested Accessories` switch off."
msgstr ""
"若要隱藏此區段，請開啟\\ :doc:`網站編輯器 <../../website/web_design>`、前往\\"
" :guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁，然後關閉\\ :guilabel:`建議配件`\\ 開關。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:188
msgid "Alternative products"
msgstr "替代產品"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:190
msgid ""
"Alternative products are displayed at the bottom of the :doc:`product page "
"<../ecommerce_design/product_page>` under the :guilabel:`Alternative "
"Products` heading."
msgstr ""
"替代產品會顯示在\\ :doc:`產品頁面 <../ecommerce_design/product_page>`\\ 底部"
"的\\ :guilabel:`替代產品`\\ 標題下方。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:0
msgid "The alternative products section of an product page."
msgstr "產品頁面的替代產品區段。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:197
msgid ""
"To customize this block, open the :doc:`website editor <../../website/"
"web_design>`, click the block on the page, and :doc:`adapt the heading and "
"text <../../website/web_design/elements>` if necessary. Go to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab, scroll to the :guilabel:`Alternative Products` "
"section, and modify the options as needed."
msgstr ""
"若要自訂此區塊，請開啟\\ :doc:`網站編輯器 <../../website/web_design>`、按一下"
"頁面上的區塊，並視需要\\ :doc:`調整標題與文字 <../../website/web_design/"
"elements>`。前往\\ :guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁，捲動至\\ :guilabel:`替代產品`\\ "
"區段，並視需要修改選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:206
msgid "Digital files"
msgstr "數位檔案"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:208
msgid ""
"It is possible to link digital files, such as certificates, eBooks, or user "
"manuals, to the products. To do so, go to the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>` and click the :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Documents` smart button. Then, click :guilabel:`Upload` to "
"upload a file directly, or for additional options, click :guilabel:`New`. "
"Choose the :guilabel:`Type` of attachment:"
msgstr ""
"您可以將數位檔案（例如證書、電子書或使用手冊）連結至產品。若要執行此操作，請"
"前往\\ :ref:`產品表單 <ecommerce/products/product-form>`\\ 並按一下\\ "
":icon:`fa-file-text-o`\\ :guilabel:`文件`\\ 智慧按鈕。接著，按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`上載`\\ 直接上載檔案，或若需要更多選項，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`新"
"增`。選擇附件的\\ :guilabel:`類型`："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:214
msgid ":guilabel:`File`: :guilabel:`Upload your file`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`檔案`：:guilabel:`上載您的檔案`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:215
msgid ":guilabel:`URL`: Insert the link to the file or media item."
msgstr ":guilabel:`網址`：插入檔案或媒體項目的連結。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:216
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cloud Storage` (if applicable): Insert a link to your cloud "
"storage to store the file on the :doc:`cloud storage </applications/general/"
"integrations/cloud_storage>` platform instead of the database’s server."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`雲端儲存`（若適用）：插入雲端儲存的連結，將檔案儲存在\\ :doc:`雲端"
"儲存 </applications/general/integrations/cloud_storage>`\\ 平台上，而非資料庫"
"的伺服器上。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:220
msgid "These documents can be made available:"
msgstr "這些文件可供使用於："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:222
msgid ""
"On the product page (before checkout): Set the :guilabel:`Sales visibility` "
"field to :guilabel:`Hidden` and enable :guilabel:`Publish on website`."
msgstr ""
"產品頁面上（結帳前）：將\\ :guilabel:`銷售可見性`\\ 欄位設為\\ :guilabel:`隱"
"藏`，並啟用\\ :guilabel:`在網站上發布`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:224
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`customer portal </applications/general/users/user_portals>` on "
"the confirmed sales order (after checkout): Set the :guilabel:`Sales "
"visibility` field to :guilabel:`On confirmed order` and "
"disable :guilabel:`Publish on website`."
msgstr ""
"已確認銷售單上的\\ :doc:`客戶門戶網站 </applications/general/users/"
"user_portals>`（結帳後）：將\\ :guilabel:`銷售可見性`\\ 欄位設為\\ "
":guilabel:`已確認訂單時`，並停用\\ :guilabel:`在網站上發布`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:229
msgid ""
"In :ref:`Kanban <studio/views/multiple-records/kanban>` view, click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`dropdown menu`) in the top-right "
"corner of the document card to :guilabel:`Edit`, :guilabel:`Delete`, "
"or :guilabel:`Download` the document."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :ref:`看板 <studio/views/multiple-records/kanban>`\\ 檢視中，按一下文件"
"卡片右上角的\\ :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v`（:guilabel:`下拉式選單`）以\\ "
":guilabel:`編輯`、:guilabel:`刪除`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`下載`\\ 文件。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:236
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "翻譯"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:238
msgid ""
"If a website is available in multiple languages, product information can be "
"translated directly on the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-"
"form>`. Fields that support multiple languages are identifiable by their "
"language abbreviation (e.g., `EN`) next to the field, such as "
"the :guilabel:`Product name`, :ref:`Out-of-Stock Message <ecommerce/products/"
"stock-management>`, the :ref:`E-Commerce Description <ecommerce/products/"
"description>`, :ref:`ribbon or badge <ecommerce/products/additional_features/"
"product-highlight>` names, :doc:`categories and variants "
"<categories_variants>` names, etc."
msgstr ""
"若網站支援多種語言，可直接在\\ :ref:`產品表單 <ecommerce/products/product-"
"form>`\\ 上翻譯產品資訊。支援多種語言的欄位可透過欄位旁的語言縮寫（例如 "
"`EN`）識別，例如\\ :guilabel:`產品名稱`、:ref:`缺貨訊息 <ecommerce/products/"
"stock-management>`、:ref:`電子商務說明 <ecommerce/products/description>"
"`、:ref:`緞帶或徽章 <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-"
"highlight>`\\ 名稱、:doc:`類別與變體 <categories_variants>`\\ 名稱等。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:247
msgid ""
"Having untranslated content on a web page may be detrimental to the user "
"experience and :doc:`SEO </applications/websites/website/structure/seo>`. To "
"avoid this, use the :ref:`Translate <translate/translate>` feature to "
"translate any remaining untranslated content on the page."
msgstr ""
"網頁上若有未翻譯的內容可能會損害使用者體驗與\\ :doc:`搜尋引擎最佳化 </"
"applications/websites/website/structure/seo>`。為避免此情況，請使用\\ "
":ref:`翻譯 <translate/translate>`\\ 功能來翻譯頁面上所有剩餘的未翻譯內容。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:253
msgid ""
":doc:`Website languages and translations </applications/websites/website/"
"configuration/translate>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`網站語言與翻譯 </applications/websites/website/configuration/translate>"
"`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:130
msgid "Stock management"
msgstr "庫存管理"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:262
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Inventory app </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` must be "
"installed to handle stock-related settings and operations."
msgstr ""
"必須安裝\\ :doc:`庫存應用程式 </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>`\\ "
"才能處理庫存相關的設定與操作。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:265
msgid ""
"To configure stock-related e-commerce options, go to :menuselection:`Website "
"--> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` "
"section, then to the :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults` subsection. The "
"following settings are available:"
msgstr ""
"若要配置庫存相關的電子商務選項，請前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 配置 --> 設"
"定`，向下捲動至\\ :guilabel:`電子商務`\\ 區段，然後至\\ :guilabel:`庫存預設"
"值`\\ 子區段。可使用以下設定："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:269
msgid ""
"If multiple :doc:`warehouses </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses>` exist, select the "
"relevant one from the :guilabel:`Warehouse` dropdown menu to set it as the "
"default."
msgstr ""
"如果存在多個\\ :doc:`倉庫 </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses>`\\ ，請從\\ :guilabel:`倉"
"庫`\\ 下拉式選單中選擇相關的倉庫，將其設為預設倉庫。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:273
msgid ""
"Next to :guilabel:`Out-of-Stock`, enable :guilabel:`Continue Selling` to "
"allow customers to place orders even when the product is out of stock. Keep "
"this option disabled to prevent customers from ordering products that are "
"out of stock."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`缺貨`\\ 旁邊，啟用\\ :guilabel:`繼續銷售`\\ 以允許客戶即使在"
"產品缺貨時也能下訂單。停用此選項以防止客戶訂購缺貨產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:276
msgid ""
"Enable the :guilabel:`Show Available Quantity` option to display the "
"remaining available quantity on the product page when it drops below a "
"defined threshold. The available quantity is calculated based on "
"the :guilabel:`On hand` quantity minus the quantity already :doc:`reserved </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"reservation_methods>` for outgoing transfers."
msgstr ""
"啟用\\ :guilabel:`顯示可用數量`\\ 選項，當可用數量低於定義的閾值時，在產品頁"
"面上顯示剩餘的可用數量。可用數量是根據\\ :guilabel:`現有量`\\ 減去已為出庫轉"
"移\\ :doc:`預留 </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/reservation_methods>`\\ 的數量計算得出的。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:282
msgid ""
"These settings apply to *all* products, but can be adapted for individual "
"products if needed. To do so, go to the product form and make sure "
"the :ref:`Track inventory option <inventory/product_management/tracking-"
"inventory>` is enabled. Then, navigate to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab and, "
"under the :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` section, enable or disable the "
"relevant :guilabel:`Sell when Out-of-Stock` and :guilabel:`Show Available "
"Qty` options. You can also compose an :guilabel:`Out-of-Stock Message` or "
"create an :ref:`out-of-stock ribbon or badge <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/product-highlight>`."
msgstr ""
"這些設定適用於*所有*產品，但如有需要，可針對個別產品進行調整。要這樣做，請前"
"往產品表單並確保已啟用\\ :ref:`追蹤庫存選項 <inventory/product_management/"
"tracking-inventory>`\\ 。然後前往\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 分頁，在\\ "
":guilabel:`電子商務商店`\\ 區段下，啟用或停用相關的\\ :guilabel:`缺貨時銷"
"售`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`顯示可用數量`\\ 選項。您也可以撰寫\\ :guilabel:`缺貨訊"
"息`\\ 或建立\\ :ref:`缺貨彩帶或標章 <ecommerce/products/additional_features/"
"product-highlight>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:291
msgid ""
"Modifying the general :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults` settings does not "
"automatically modify the related option(s) on the product form for existing "
"products; it only affects products created after the feature is enabled/"
"disabled."
msgstr ""
"修改一般\\ :guilabel:`庫存預設值`\\ 設定不會自動修改現有產品之產品表單上的相"
"關選項；它僅影響在啟用/停用功能後建立的產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:294
msgid ""
"To display the stock level on the product page, the :guilabel:`Product Type` "
"field on the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>` must be "
"set to :guilabel:`Goods` or :guilabel:`Combo`."
msgstr ""
"要在產品頁面上顯示庫存水準，:ref:`產品表單 <ecommerce/products/product-form>"
"`\\ 上的\\ :guilabel:`產品類型`\\ 欄位必須設為\\ :guilabel:`商品`\\ 或\\ "
":guilabel:`組合`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:297
msgid ""
"A :icon:`fa-envelope-o` (:guilabel:`envelope`) :guilabel:`Get notified when "
"back in stock` button appears on the product page when an item is out of "
"stock. Customers can click the link to enter their email address and receive "
"a notification once the item is back in stock."
msgstr ""
"當商品缺貨時，產品頁面上會顯示\\ :icon:`fa-envelope-o`\\ （\\ :guilabel:`信"
"封`\\ ）\\ :guilabel:`到貨時通知我`\\ 按鈕。客戶可以按一下該連結輸入電子郵件"
"地址，並在商品到貨時收到通知。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:301
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`Click & Collect <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>` feature is "
"enabled, the product availability is displayed on the product page based on "
"the stock in the warehouse defined on the related :doc:`delivery method </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>` form."
msgstr ""
"如果啟用了\\ :ref:`線上下單到店取貨 <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>`\\ 功"
"能，產品頁面上會根據相關\\ :doc:`配送方法 </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>`\\ 表單"
"上定義的倉庫之庫存顯示產品可用性。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:308
msgid ""
"Currently, the `Boko Chair` is not available in any warehouses. However, "
"customers can click the :icon:`fa-envelope-o` "
"(:guilabel:`envelope`) :guilabel:`Get notified when back in stock` link to "
"receive a notification as soon as the product becomes available again. "
"An :guilabel:`Out-of-Stock Message` can also be added to inform customers "
"that the item will be replenished."
msgstr ""
"目前，`Boko Chair`在任何倉庫中都沒有庫存。但是，客戶可以按一下\\ :icon:`fa-"
"envelope-o`（:guilabel:`信封`）:guilabel:`補貨時通知我`\\ 連結，以便在產品再"
"次到貨時立即收到通知。也可以加入\\ :guilabel:`缺貨訊息`\\ 來通知客戶該商品將"
"會補貨。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:0
msgid ""
"Example of a product that is out of stock, but which will be available again."
msgstr "缺貨但將再次到貨的產品範例。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:318
msgid ""
"If a unique reference is needed for inventory management, install "
"the :doc:`Manufacturing app </applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing>` "
"and create :doc:`kit bills of materials </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"manufacturing/advanced_configuration/kit_shipping>`. Each kit links its "
"published \"virtual\" products to the main reference tracked in Inventory. "
"This ensures that any item sold on the website is converted into the "
"corresponding stocked item in the delivery order."
msgstr ""
"如果庫存管理需要唯一的參考編號，請安裝\\ :doc:`製造應用程式 </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing>`\\ 並建立\\ :doc:`套件物料清單 </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/advanced_configuration/"
"kit_shipping>`\\ 。每個套件將其發布的「虛擬」產品連結到庫存中追蹤的主要參考編"
"號。這可確保在網站上銷售的任何商品都會在交貨單中轉換為相應的庫存商品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:328
msgid "Packagings"
msgstr "包裝"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:330
msgid ""
"To offer different product pack sizes to customers on the e-commerce, "
"configure product :doc:`packagings </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/product_management/configure/packaging>`. Then go to "
"the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>` and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab. Under :guilabel:`Upsell & cross-sell`, add as "
"many package types as needed in the :guilabel:`Packagings` field. The "
"available package types are displayed on the e-commerce :doc:`product page "
"<../ecommerce_design/product_page>`."
msgstr ""
"要在電子商務網站上向客戶提供不同的產品包裝尺寸，請配置產品\\ :doc:`包裝 </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
"packaging>`\\ 。然後前往\\ :ref:`產品表單 <ecommerce/products/product-form>"
"`\\ 並前往\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 分頁。在\\ :guilabel:`追加銷售與交叉銷售`\\ "
"下，在\\ :guilabel:`包裝`\\ 欄位中加入所需數量的包裝類型。可用的包裝類型會顯"
"示在電子商務\\ :doc:`產品頁面 <../ecommerce_design/product_page>`\\ 上。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:None
msgid "Product packages on the e-commerce page."
msgstr "電子商務頁面上的產品包裝。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:342
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add packagings to a specific :ref:`product variant "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>`. To do so, go to the "
"product form, click the :icon:`fa-sitemap` :guilabel:`Variants` :ref:`smart "
"button <products/variants/variants-smart-button>`, and select the relevant "
"product variant. Under :guilabel:`Sales`, add as many package types as "
"needed in the :guilabel:`Packagings` field."
msgstr ""
"也可以為特定\\ :ref:`產品變體 <ecommerce/categories_variants/product-"
"variants>`\\ 加入包裝。若要執行此操作，請前往產品表單，按一下\\ :icon:`fa-"
"sitemap`\\ \\ :guilabel:`變體`\\ \\ :ref:`智慧按鈕 <products/variants/"
"variants-smart-button>`\\ ，然後選擇相關產品變體。在\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 下"
"，在\\ :guilabel:`包裝`\\ 欄位中加入所需數量的包裝類型。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:9
msgid ""
"Customize the design of the :doc:`product pages <../ecommerce/"
"ecommerce_design/product_page>`, structure the :doc:`product catalog <../"
"ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>` and use :doc:`additional features <../"
"ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features>` to improve the customer's "
"shopping experience."
msgstr ""
"可自訂\\ :doc:`產品頁面 <../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page>`\\ 的設"
"計、建構\\ :doc:`產品目錄 <../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>`，並使用\\ "
":doc:`附加功能 <../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features>`\\ 來改善"
"客戶的購物體驗。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:16
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:27
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:63
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:3
msgid "Product page"
msgstr "產品頁面"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:16
msgid ""
"Design the product pages by showcasing product details and additional "
"information, customizing product images and videos, and adding content and "
"design elements using building blocks."
msgstr ""
"透過展示產品詳情和其他資訊、自訂產品圖片和影片，以及使用建構區塊加入內容和設"
"計元素，來設計產品頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:23
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:3
msgid "Product catalog"
msgstr "產品目錄"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:23
msgid ""
"Organize the product catalog by customizing the layout, using categories, "
"and adding building blocks, and filtering options."
msgstr "透過自訂版面配置、使用類別、加入建構區塊及篩選選項，來組織產品目錄。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:30
msgid ""
"Enable additional features, such as the wishlist and product comparison, and "
"highlight products using ribbons."
msgstr "啟用附加功能（例如願望清單和產品比較），並使用緞帶來突顯產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce provides additional features for online shops, including "
"a :ref:`product comparison <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-"
"comparison>` tool, a :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/additional_features/"
"wishlists>`, and :ref:`product highlight options <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/product-highlight>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 電子商務為線上商店提供額外功能，包括\\ :ref:`產品比較 <ecommerce/"
"products/additional_features/product-comparison>`\\ 工具、:ref:`願望清單 "
"<ecommerce/products/additional_features/wishlists>`\\ 以及\\ :ref:`產品重點選"
"項 <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-highlight>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:13
msgid "Product comparison"
msgstr "產品比較"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:15
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Add to compare`) button allows website "
"visitors to compare products based on their :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/attributes>`. Customers can click this button to select "
"the products they wish to compare, then click :guilabel:`Compare` in the pop-"
"up window at the bottom of the page to see the comparison summary."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-exchange`（:guilabel:`加入比較`）按鈕允許網站訪客根據產品的\\ "
":ref:`屬性 <ecommerce/categories_variants/attributes>`\\ 進行比較。客戶可以按"
"一下此按鈕以選擇想要比較的產品，然後在頁面底部的彈出視窗中按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`比較`\\ 來查看比較摘要。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:None
msgid "Product comparison window"
msgstr "產品比較視窗"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:23
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:59
msgid ""
"This button can be enabled independently in different sections of the "
"website:"
msgstr "此按鈕可在網站的不同區段中獨立啟用："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:29
msgid ""
"Go to a product page, open the website editor, go to the :guilabel:`Style` "
"tab, navigate to the :guilabel:`Products Details` section, and toggle "
"the :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` button. Once done, it becomes "
"available on each product page that has attributes."
msgstr ""
"前往產品頁面，開啟網站編輯器，前往\\ :guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁，導覽至\\ "
":guilabel:`產品詳細資料`\\ 區段，並切換\\ :icon:`fa-exchange`\\ "
"（:guilabel:`比較`）按鈕。完成後，它會在每個具有屬性的產品頁面上可用。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:34
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:69
msgid "Catalog page"
msgstr "目錄頁面"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:36
msgid ""
"To display the :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) button on "
"the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`, open the website "
"editor, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and click the :icon:`fa-paint-"
"brush` (:guilabel:`paint brush`) icon next to :guilabel:`Product Design`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Actions` section, toggle the :icon:`fa-exchange` "
"(:guilabel:`Compare`) button, and choose between :guilabel:`Inline` "
"and :guilabel:`On Hover`."
msgstr ""
"若要在\\ :ref:`商店頁面 <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`\\ 上顯示\\ "
":icon:`fa-exchange`\\ （:guilabel:`比較`）按鈕，請開啟網站編輯器，前往\\ "
":guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`產品設計`\\ 旁邊的\\ "
":icon:`fa-paint-brush`\\ （:guilabel:`畫筆`）圖示。在\\ :guilabel:`動作`\\ 區"
"段中，切換\\ :icon:`fa-exchange`\\ （:guilabel:`比較`）按鈕，並在\\ "
":guilabel:`內嵌`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`懸停時顯示`\\ 之間選擇。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:44
msgid "You can only compare a maximum of four products at a time."
msgstr "您一次最多只能比較四個產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:47
msgid ""
"Define :ref:`attribute categories <ecommerce/categories_variants/attribute-"
"categories>` to group similar attributes under the same section when "
"comparing products."
msgstr ""
"定義\\ :ref:`屬性類別 <ecommerce/categories_variants/attribute-categories>`，"
"以便在比較產品時將類似屬性歸入同一部分。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:53
msgid "Wishlist"
msgstr "願望清單"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:55
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Add to wishlist`) button allows customers "
"to add products to their wishlist, i.e., save them for later. It is enabled "
"by default and available on each product page."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-heart-o`（:guilabel:`加入願望清單`）按鈕可讓顧客將產品加入願望清單"
"，即儲存以供稍後使用。此功能預設為啟用，並可在每個產品頁面上使用。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:65
msgid ""
"Go to a product page, open the website editor, go to the :guilabel:`Style` "
"tab, navigate to the :guilabel:`Products Details` section, and toggle "
"the :icon:`fa-heart` :guilabel:`Wishlist` button. Once done, it becomes "
"available on each product page."
msgstr ""
"前往產品頁面，開啟網站編輯器，前往\\ :guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁，導覽至\\ "
":guilabel:`產品詳細資訊`\\ 區段，然後切換\\ :icon:`fa-heart`\\ :guilabel:`願"
"望清單`\\ 按鈕。完成後，該按鈕將在每個產品頁面上可用。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:71
msgid ""
"To display the :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`) button on "
"the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`, open the website "
"editor, go to :guilabel:`Style`, and click the :icon:`fa-paint-brush` "
"(:guilabel:`paint brush`) icon next to :guilabel:`Product Design`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Actions` section, toggle the :icon:`fa-heart` "
"(:guilabel:`Wishlist`) button and choose between :guilabel:`Fixed` "
"and :guilabel:`Fixed - On Hover`."
msgstr ""
"若要在\\ :ref:`商店頁面 <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`\\ 上顯示\\ "
":icon:`fa-heart-o`（:guilabel:`願望清單`）按鈕，請開啟網站編輯器，前往\\ "
":guilabel:`樣式`，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`產品設計`\\ 旁邊的\\ :icon:`fa-"
"paint-brush`（:guilabel:`油漆刷`）圖示。在\\ :guilabel:`動作`\\ 區段中，切"
"換\\ :icon:`fa-heart`（:guilabel:`願望清單`）按鈕，並在\\ :guilabel:`固定`\\ "
"與\\ :guilabel:`固定 - 滑鼠懸停時`\\ 之間進行選擇。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:78
msgid "Header"
msgstr "頁首"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:80
msgid ""
"To display the :icon:`fa-heart` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`) icon in the header, "
"open the website editor, click the header, navigate to the :guilabel:`Show/"
"Hide Elements` section, and toggle the :icon:`fa-heart` "
"(:guilabel:`Wishlist`) icon next to :guilabel:`Show Empty`. If it is not "
"enabled, the wishlist icon only appears when an item has been added to the "
"wishlist. The number of items in the wishlist is also displayed next to the "
"icon."
msgstr ""
"若要在頁首中顯示\\ :icon:`fa-heart`（:guilabel:`願望清單`）圖示，請開啟網站編"
"輯器，按一下頁首，導覽至\\ :guilabel:`顯示/隱藏元素`\\ 區段，然後切換\\ "
":guilabel:`顯示空白`\\ 旁邊的\\ :icon:`fa-heart`（:guilabel:`願望清單`）圖示"
"。如果未啟用，則願望清單圖示僅在項目已加入願望清單時顯示。願望清單中的項目數"
"量也會顯示在圖示旁邊。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:87
msgid "Wishlist page"
msgstr "願望清單頁面"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:89
msgid ""
"It is possible to customize the layout of the :guilabel:`My Wishlist` page. "
"To do so, open the website editor while on the wishlist page, and in "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab under the :guilabel:`Wishlist Page` section, "
"choose a :guilabel:`Products Design`. Depending on the selected design, "
"adapt the layout according to :guilabel:`Desktop` or :guilabel:`Mobile` "
"devices. Click the :icon:`fa-paint-brush` (:guilabel:`paint brush`) icon "
"next to :guilabel:`Products Design` to access more customization options."
msgstr ""
"可自訂\\ :guilabel:`我的願望清單`\\ 頁面的版面配置。若要執行此操作，請在願望"
"清單頁面上開啟網站編輯器，然後在\\ :guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁的\\ :guilabel:`願"
"望清單頁面`\\ 區段下，選擇\\ :guilabel:`產品設計`。根據所選的設計，依據\\ "
":guilabel:`桌面`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`行動`\\ 裝置調整版面配置。按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`產品設計`\\ 旁邊的\\ :icon:`fa-paint-brush`（:guilabel:`油漆刷`）"
"圖示以存取更多自訂選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:97
msgid ""
"Customers can move products from their cart to their wishlist by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Save for later` button in the :guilabel:`Order "
"summary` :ref:`checkout step <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`."
msgstr ""
"顧客可以在\\ :guilabel:`訂單摘要`\\ :ref:`結帳步驟 <ecommerce/checkout/"
"review_order>`\\ 中按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存以供稍後使用`\\ 按鈕，將產品從購物"
"車移至願望清單。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:100
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`My Wishlist` page, customers can move products from their "
"wishlist to the cart."
msgstr "在\\ :guilabel:`我的願望清單`\\ 頁面上，顧客可以將產品從願望清單移至購物車。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:106
msgid "Product highlight"
msgstr "產品亮點"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:108
msgid ""
"The eCommerce app allows you to highlight products to increase their "
"visibility. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Product Ribbons`. You can either use one of the preconfigured ribbons "
"(:guilabel:`Sold out`, :guilabel:`Sale`, :guilabel:`Out of stock` "
"or :guilabel:`New!`) or create a :guilabel:`New` one. Add a ribbon name, and "
"select the method to :guilabel:`Assign` it:"
msgstr ""
"電子商務應用程式可讓您突顯產品以提高其可見度。若要執行此操作，請前往\\ "
":menuselection:`網站 --> 電子商務 --> 產品緞帶`。您可以使用其中一個預先配置的"
"緞帶（:guilabel:`已售完`、:guilabel:`促銷`、:guilabel:`缺貨`\\ 或\\ "
":guilabel:`新品！`），或建立\\ :guilabel:`新`\\ 緞帶。加入緞帶名稱，並選擇\\ "
":guilabel:`指派`\\ 方法："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:114
msgid ":guilabel:`Manually`: assign the ribbon manually."
msgstr ":guilabel:`手動`：手動指派緞帶。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Sale`: the ribbon is displayed when the product is on sale, "
"e.g., when using a :ref:`comparison price <ecommerce/prices/permanent-"
"discounts>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`促銷中`：當產品促銷時顯示緞帶，例如使用\\ :ref:`比較價格 "
"<ecommerce/prices/permanent-discounts>`\\ 時。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`When New`: the ribbon is displayed when a new product is added. "
"Specify the number of :guilabel:`days after publication` it should be "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`新品時`：當加入新產品時顯示緞帶。指定應顯示的\\ :guilabel:`發佈後"
"天數`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`when out of stock`: the ribbon is displayed when the product is "
"currently no longer available."
msgstr ":guilabel:`缺貨時`：當產品目前不再可用時顯示緞帶。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:122
msgid ""
"Choose its :guilabel:`Position`, either :guilabel:`Left` "
"or :guilabel:`Right`, and a :guilabel:`Style`, either :guilabel:`Ribbon` "
"or :guilabel:`Badge`. Define the :guilabel:`Text Color` and "
"the :guilabel:`Background Color`. Then :guilabel:`Save`. The ribbon is now "
"available for all the e-commerce products."
msgstr ""
"選擇其\\ :guilabel:`位置`（可為\\ :guilabel:`左`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`右`）以"
"及\\ :guilabel:`樣式`（可為\\ :guilabel:`Ribbon`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`Badge`）。"
"定義\\ :guilabel:`文字顏色`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`背景顏色`。然後\\ :guilabel:`儲"
"存`。該彩帶現在可用於所有電子商務產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:None
msgid "Product with badge"
msgstr "帶有徽章的產品"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:131
msgid "There are other ways to create a new product ribbon:"
msgstr "還有其他方式可建立新的產品緞帶："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:133
msgid ""
"Access the product form, and under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, change or "
"create the ribbon in the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field."
msgstr ""
"存取產品表單，並在\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 分頁下，於\\ :guilabel:`緞帶`\\ 欄位"
"中變更或建立緞帶。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:135
msgid ""
"Edit/create ribbons from the :doc:`website editor <../../website/"
"web_design>`. To do so, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Product Details` section. Click the green :icon:`fa-plus` "
"(:guilabel:`Create`) icon next to the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field or "
"the :icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` (:guilabel:`Edit`) icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`Ribbon` label. The :guilabel:`Assign` feature is not "
"available for configuration in the website editor."
msgstr ""
"從\\ :doc:`網站編輯器 <../../website/web_design>`\\ 編輯/建立緞帶。若要執行此"
"操作，請前往\\ :guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁，並導覽至\\ :guilabel:`產品詳細資訊`\\"
" 區段。按一下\\ :guilabel:`緞帶`\\ 欄位旁邊的綠色\\ :icon:`fa-"
"plus`（:guilabel:`建立`）圖示，或按一下\\ :guilabel:`緞帶`\\ 標籤旁邊的\\ "
":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o`（:guilabel:`編輯`）圖示。:guilabel:`指派`\\ 功能無"
"法在網站編輯器中進行配置。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:0
msgid "Create a new ribbon in the website editor"
msgstr "在網站編輯器中建立新緞帶"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:145
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add ribbons for specific :ref:`product variants "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>`. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and select a product. "
"Click the :guilabel:`Variants` smart button, choose a variant, and add a "
"ribbon in the :guilabel:`Variant Ribbon` field of the :guilabel:`Sales` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"也可以為特定的\\ :ref:`產品變體 <ecommerce/categories_variants/product-"
"variants>`\\ 加入彩帶。若要這樣做，請前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 電子商"
"務 --> 產品`\\ 並選擇一個產品。按一下\\ :guilabel:`變體`\\ 智慧按鈕，選擇一個"
"變體，然後在\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 區段的\\ :guilabel:`變體彩帶`\\ 欄位中加入"
"彩帶。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:5
msgid ""
"The e-commerce catalog displays products for customers to browse. It is "
"organized using :ref:`product categories <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"categories>`, available :ref:`product variants <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/product-variants>`, sorting options, and navigation "
"paths. Essentially, the e-commerce catalog is the shop page of your website."
msgstr ""
"電子商務目錄顯示產品供客戶瀏覽。它使用\\ :ref:`產品類別 <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/categories>`、可用的\\ :ref:`產品變體 <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/product-variants>`、排序選項和導覽路徑進行組織。基本上，"
"電子商務目錄就是您網站的商店頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:10
msgid ""
"The product catalog features a :ref:`toolbar and some filters <ecommerce/"
"catalog/toolbar-and-filters>` in the sidebar (or slide-out menu), along with "
"a dedicated :ref:`product listing area <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`. "
"Additionally, the shop and category pages' :ref:`layout <ecommerce/catalog/"
"customize-layout>`, as well as the :ref:`e-commerce footer <ecommerce/"
"catalog/footer>`, can be customized, and you can add :ref:`building blocks "
"<ecommerce/catalog/catalog-blocks>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"產品目錄包含側邊欄（或滑出選單）中的\\ :ref:`工具列和篩選器 <ecommerce/"
"catalog/toolbar-and-filters>`，以及專用的\\ :ref:`產品清單區域 <ecommerce/"
"catalog/product-listing>`。此外，商店和類別頁面的\\ :ref:`版面配置 "
"<ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`以及\\ :ref:`電子商務頁尾 <ecommerce/"
"catalog/footer>`都可以自訂，您也可以根據需要加入\\ :ref:`建置區塊 <ecommerce/"
"catalog/catalog-blocks>`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:17
msgid ""
"To customize the catalog, go to the shop page, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the "
"upper-right corner, select the section you want to change, and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab."
msgstr ""
"若要自訂目錄，請前往商店頁面，按一下右上角的\\ :guilabel:`編輯`，選擇您要變更"
"的區段，然後導覽至\\ :guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:23
msgid "Toolbar and filters"
msgstr "工具列和篩選器"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:25
msgid ""
"The toolbar and sidebar (or slide-out menu) provide advanced filtering tools "
"to help customers search and navigate the product catalog "
"using :ref:`categories <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` and :ref:`attributes "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>`."
msgstr ""
"工具列和側邊欄（或滑出選單）提供進階篩選工具，協助客戶使用\\ :ref:`類別 "
"<ecommerce/catalog/categories>`和\\ :ref:`屬性 <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>"
"`搜尋和導覽產品目錄。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you do not want to display a toolbar or sidebar, disable all related "
"options in the website editor, :ref:`hide attributes <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/attributes>`, and make sure to only assign one pricelist "
"to the website."
msgstr ""
"如果您不想顯示工具列或側邊欄，請在網站編輯器中停用所有相關選項、\\ :ref:`隱藏"
"屬性 <ecommerce/categories_variants/attributes>`，並確保僅將一個價目表指派給"
"網站。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:37
msgid "Categories"
msgstr "類別"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:39
msgid ""
"To create a :ref:`category <ecommerce/categories_variants/categories>` quick "
"access in the toolbar or general access in the sidebar, click "
"the :guilabel:`Top` and/or :guilabel:`Sidebar` button next "
"to :guilabel:`Categories`, and choose a :guilabel:`Style` for them. When "
"the :guilabel:`Sidebar` is selected, the option :guilabel:`Collapse Category "
"Recursive` appears, allowing you to collapse the category in the sidebar."
msgstr ""
"若要在工具列中建立\\ :ref:`類別 <ecommerce/categories_variants/categories>`快"
"速存取或在側邊欄中建立一般存取，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`類別`旁邊的\\ "
":guilabel:`頂端`和/或\\ :guilabel:`側邊欄`按鈕，然後為其選擇\\ :guilabel:`樣"
"式`。當選取\\ :guilabel:`側邊欄`時，會出現\\ :guilabel:`摺疊遞迴類別`選項，讓"
"您可以在側邊欄中摺疊類別。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:49
msgid ""
"The category filters located in the sidebar are not affected by "
"the :guilabel:`Filters` setting."
msgstr "位於側邊欄中的類別篩選器不受\\ :guilabel:`篩選器`設定的影響。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:54
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "工具列"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:56
msgid ""
"It is possible to display a search bar or sort-by options in the toolbar of "
"the shop page by clicking the :guilabel:`Sort By` and/or :guilabel:`Search` "
"buttons next to the :guilabel:`Toolbar` label. Toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Floating` switch on to always display the search bar, "
"the :ref:`pricelist selector <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` (if any), and "
"sort-by options at the bottom of the window, even when scrolling, and select "
"a :guilabel:`Default Sort` option."
msgstr ""
"您可以按一下\\ :guilabel:`工具列`標籤旁邊的\\ :guilabel:`排序依據`和/或\\ "
":guilabel:`搜尋`按鈕，在商店頁面的工具列中顯示搜尋列或排序依據選項。開啟\\ "
":guilabel:`浮動`開關，即可在視窗底部始終顯示搜尋列、\\ :ref:`價目表選擇器 "
"<ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`（如有）和排序依據選項（即使在捲動時也會顯示）"
"，並選取\\ :guilabel:`預設排序`選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:63
msgid ""
"The default sort applies to *all* :ref:`categories <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/categories>`."
msgstr ""
"預設排序適用於*所有*\\ :ref:`類別 <ecommerce/categories_variants/categories>"
"`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:68
msgid "Filters"
msgstr "篩選器"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:70
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Filters` field to:"
msgstr "將\\ :guilabel:`篩選器`欄位設定為："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:72
msgid ":guilabel:`Sidebar`: to display filters in the side panel;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`側邊欄`：在側邊面板中顯示篩選器；"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:73
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Off-screen menu`: to display filters in a slide-out menu that "
"opens when clicking the :icon:`fa-sliders` :guilabel:`Filters` button in the "
"toolbar;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`螢幕外選單`：在滑出選單中顯示篩選器，按一下工具列中的\\ :icon:`fa-"
"sliders`\\ :guilabel:`篩選器`按鈕時開啟；"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:75
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide`: to hide filters entirely."
msgstr ":guilabel:`隱藏`：完全隱藏篩選器。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:77
msgid "By default, two :guilabel:`Filters` are enabled:"
msgstr "預設啟用兩個\\ :guilabel:`篩選器`："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Price`: Use the switch to display a :guilabel:`Price Range` bar, "
"which allows customers to filter products according to a specific price "
"range by dragging adjustable handles."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`價格`：使用開關顯示\\ :guilabel:`價格範圍`列，讓客戶透過拖曳可調整"
"的控點，根據特定價格範圍篩選產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Toggle the switch to display product :guilabel:`Tags` on "
"the shop page, and allow customers to filter products using those tags by "
"going to the :guilabel:`Tags` section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`標籤`：切換開關以在商店頁面上顯示產品\\ :guilabel:`標籤`，並前往\\"
" :guilabel:`標籤`區段，讓客戶使用這些標籤篩選產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:87
msgid ""
"To create product tags on your e-commerce, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Product Tags`, and click :guilabel:`New`. Add "
"a :guilabel:`Tag` name, toggle the :guilabel:`Visible to customers` switch, "
"and select a :guilabel:`Color`. Optionally, add an image. Then go to the "
"product form, and assign the relevant tags where needed."
msgstr ""
"若要在電子商務建立產品標籤，前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 電子商務 --> "
"Product Tags`\\ ，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 。加入\\ :guilabel:`Tag`\\ "
"名稱，切換\\ :guilabel:`Visible to customers`\\ 開關，並選擇\\ :guilabel:`顏"
"色`\\ 。您也可以加入圖片。接著前往產品表單，並在需要的地方指派相關標籤。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:92
msgid ""
"For :doc:`rental products <../../../sales/rental>`, you can also add "
"a :guilabel:`Rental Date` option to display a date range calendar to check "
"their availability over a specific period."
msgstr ""
"對於\\ :doc:`租賃產品 <../../../sales/rental>`\\ ，您也可以加入\\ "
":guilabel:`Rental Date`\\ 選項，以顯示日期範圍日曆來檢查其在特定期間內的可用"
"性。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:100
msgid ""
"When you offer :ref:`product variants <ecommerce/categories_variants/product-"
"variants>` with different :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"attributes>`, those options appear in the sidebar or slide-out menu when "
"filters are shown. The menu automatically adapts to the number of attribute "
"sections:"
msgstr ""
"當您提供具有不同\\ :ref:`屬性 <ecommerce/categories_variants/attributes>`\\ "
"的\\ :ref:`產品子類 <ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>`\\ 時，"
"這些選項會在顯示篩選條件時出現在側邊欄或滑出選單中。選單會自動根據屬性區段的"
"數量調整："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:105
msgid "**Up to 4 attributes**: all the attribute values are displayed."
msgstr "**最多 4 個屬性**：顯示所有屬性值。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:106
msgid "**More than 4 attributes**: the sections are automatically collapsed."
msgstr "**超過 4 個屬性**：區段會自動摺疊。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:109
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Radio` and :guilabel:`Select` :ref:`display types <products/"
"variants/attributes>`, a :guilabel:`View More` button appears when there are "
"more than **8** values, and a search field when the number of values exceeds "
"**20**."
msgstr ""
"對於\\ :guilabel:`Radio`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`Select`\\ \\ :ref:`display types "
"<products/variants/attributes>`\\ ，當數值超過 **8** 個時會出現\\ "
":guilabel:`View More`\\ 按鈕，當數值超過 **20** 個時會出現搜尋欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:112
msgid ""
"At least two attribute values are required for the filter to be visible."
msgstr "至少需要兩個屬性值才能顯示篩選條件。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:113
msgid ""
"The attribute filters located in the sidebar or slide-out menu are affected "
"by the :guilabel:`Filters` setting."
msgstr ""
"位於側邊欄或滑出選單中的屬性篩選條件會受到\\ :guilabel:`Filters`\\ 設定的影響"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:117
msgid ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:118
msgid ":doc:`../../ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:123
msgid "Product listing area"
msgstr "產品清單區域"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:127
msgid ""
"Define the number of products to display on your shop pages by configuring "
"the :guilabel:`Size` displayed per page and line, and specify the number of "
"columns for :guilabel:`Mobile` devices."
msgstr ""
"透過設定每頁和每行顯示的\\ :guilabel:`大小`\\ ，以及指定\\ "
":guilabel:`Mobile`\\ 裝置的欄數，來定義商店頁面上顯示的產品數量。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:131
msgid ""
"The number of products displayed on a page may affect performance and page "
"loading speed."
msgstr "頁面上顯示的產品數量可能會影響效能和頁面載入速度。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:133
msgid ""
"In addition, you can manually change a product’s position on the shop page "
"or product category page. To do so, click a specific product, change "
"its :guilabel:`Size`, and :guilabel:`Re-order` it using the arrows in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` section of the :guilabel:`Style` tab. The :icon:`fa-"
"angle-double-left` (:guilabel:`double left arrow`) and :icon:`fa-angle-"
"double-right` (:guilabel:`double right arrow`) buttons allow you to move the "
"product to the extreme left or right, and the :icon:`fa-angle-left` "
"(:guilabel:`single left arrow`) and :icon:`fa-angle-right` "
"(:guilabel:`single right arrow`) buttons allow you to move it one row to the "
"left or right. You can also choose or create a :ref:`ribbon or badge "
"<ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-highlight>` to highlight a "
"specific product."
msgstr ""
"此外，您可以手動變更產品在商店頁面或產品類別頁面上的位置。若要這樣做，按一下"
"特定產品，變更其\\ :guilabel:`大小`\\ ，並在\\ :guilabel:`樣式`\\ 分頁的\\ "
":guilabel:`產品`\\ 區段中使用箭頭\\ :guilabel:`重新排序`\\ 。\\ :icon:`fa-"
"angle-double-left`\\ （\\ :guilabel:`double left arrow`\\ ）和\\ :icon:`fa-"
"angle-double-right`\\ （\\ :guilabel:`double right arrow`\\ ）按鈕可讓您將產"
"品移至最左側或最右側，而\\ :icon:`fa-angle-left`\\ （\\ :guilabel:`single "
"left arrow`\\ ）和\\ :icon:`fa-angle-right`\\ （\\ :guilabel:`single right "
"arrow`\\ ）按鈕可讓您將其向左或向右移動一行。您也可以選擇或建立\\ "
":ref:`ribbon or badge <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-"
"highlight>`\\ 來突顯特定產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:144
msgid ""
"It is also possible to change the products' positions on the shop page by "
"going to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`, switching to "
"the list view, and dragging and dropping the products within the list."
msgstr ""
"您也可以透過前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 電子商務 --> 產品`\\ ，切換至清單"
"檢視，並在清單中拖放產品，來變更產品在商店頁面上的位置。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:151
msgid "Product card design"
msgstr "產品卡片設計"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:153
msgid ""
"To customize the product cards' design, choose a :guilabel:`Products "
"Design`, click the :icon:`fa-paint-brush` :guilabel:`(paint brush)` icon "
"next to it to:"
msgstr ""
"若要自訂產品卡片的設計，選擇\\ :guilabel:`Products Design`\\ ，按一下旁邊的\\"
" :icon:`fa-paint-brush`\\ \\ :guilabel:`(paint brush)`\\ 圖示以："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:156
msgid "Choose a :guilabel:`Preset` layout;"
msgstr "選擇\\ :guilabel:`Preset`\\ 版面配置；"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:157
msgid "Adapt the :guilabel:`General` design;"
msgstr "調整\\ :guilabel:`General`\\ 設計；"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:158
msgid ""
"Customize the :guilabel:`Text & content` (e.g., show "
"a :guilabel:`Description`, and :guilabel:`Ratings`);"
msgstr ""
"自訂\\ :guilabel:`Text & content`\\ （例如顯示\\ :guilabel:`Description`\\ "
"和\\ :guilabel:`Ratings`\\ ）；"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:160
msgid ""
"Customize the :guilabel:`Images`' layout (e.g., enable :guilabel:`Secondary "
"Image` to show a second image when hovering over the product image on the "
"shop or category page);"
msgstr ""
"自訂\\ :guilabel:`Images`\\ 的版面配置（例如啟用\\ :guilabel:`Secondary "
"Image`\\ 以在商店或類別頁面上將滑鼠懸停在產品圖片上時顯示第二張圖片）；"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:162
msgid ""
"Enable some :guilabel:`Actions` (e.g., :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` :ref:`Add to "
"cart <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>`, :icon:`fa-exchange` :ref:`Compare "
"<ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-comparison>`, or :icon:`fa-"
"heart` :ref:`Wishlist <ecommerce/products/additional_features/wishlists>`) "
"and customize their placement."
msgstr ""
"啟用一些\\ :guilabel:`Actions`\\ （例如\\ :icon:`fa-shopping-cart`\\ \\ "
":ref:`加入購物車 <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>`\\ 、\\ :icon:`fa-"
"exchange`\\ \\ :ref:`Compare <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-"
"comparison>`\\ 或\\ :icon:`fa-heart`\\ \\ :ref:`願望清單 <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>`\\ ）並自訂其位置。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:168
msgid ""
"You can also add a :ref:`variant picture <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"attributes>` on the product card."
msgstr ""
"您也可以在產品卡片上加入\\ :ref:`變體圖片 <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"attributes>`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:174
msgid "Shop and category page design"
msgstr "商店與類別頁面設計"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:176
msgid ""
"The design of the shop and individual category pages can be customized as "
"follows:"
