msgstr ""
"選擇在產品頁面的\\ :guilabel:`規格`\\ 區段中顯示產品\\ :ref:`屬性 <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/attributes>`\\ 的方式："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:105
