":guilabel:`Advanced`\\ 區段，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`Code Injection`\\ 旁邊"
"的\\ :guilabel:`<head>`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`</body>`\\ 以貼上程式碼，然後按一"
"下\\ :guilabel:`Save`\\ 。"

